		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think my tests never became conclusive enough on the issue. I wanted to determine all power-up behavior but it proved to be more complex than I was willing to probe. The most recent test code I have from October 2005 is commented with this: "The VBL flag ($2002 bit 7) is set at power-up and clear at reset. It is next set about 27384 clocks later." I probably posted about this in another thread last year when I was testing it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
